Business Brief -- Sonex Research Inc.:
   President Peter Mills Has
   Equivalent of 12.9% Stake
The filing said Mr. Mills also holds 250,000 preferred
shares, representing 12.5% of total preferred shares
outstanding.
   In addition, upon Mr. Mills's election as chief executive
this month, options for the purchase of 146,111 shares became
exercisable within the next 60 days.
   According to the filing, the shares were acquired for
investment reasons.